title: Fine-Knit Skirt
schema_description: Fine-knit, calf-length skirt with a high waist and elasticized waistband. Visible, vertical seams at front, one finishing in a slit.

title: Voluminous Skirt
schema_description: Loose-fit, calf-length skirt in woven fabric with a slight sheen. High waist, elasticized waistband with gathers, and a voluminous silhouette. Unlined.

title: Mini Skort
schema_description: Mini skort in woven fabric. High waist, wrapover front with a fastener at one side, and a concealed zipper at one side with hook-and-eye fastener. Mock welt back pocket.

title: Pleated Mini Skort
schema_description: Mini skort in woven fabric. Regular waist, zipper at one side with hook-and-eye fastener, inverted box pleats at front, and mock welt back pockets.

title: Double-Waistband Pencil Skirt
schema_description: Calf-length skirt in woven fabric with an elasticized, contrasting extended waistband. Mock fly with hook-and-bar fastener, concealed zipper at one side, diagonal side pockets, and welt back pockets. Vent at back.

title: Interlock Skort
schema_description: Short, wrap-front skort in thick interlock jersey. High waist, concealed, elasticized waistband, and darts at back. Metal button at front and a mock welt pocket.

title: Fine-Knit Midi Skirt
schema_description: Fine-knit, calf-length A-line skirt with visible, vertical seams at front and back. Regular waist and concealed elastic at waistband.

title: Belt-Detail Midi Skirt
schema_description: A-line, calf-length skirt in thick jersey. High waist, elasticized waistband, and decorative belt with a metal buckle. Raw edge at hem.

title: Pleated Tennis Skirt with DryMove™
schema_description: Pleated tennis skirt in functional fabric made with DryMove™ to wick away moisture from skin and keep you comfortably dry while moving. High waist with elasticized waistband. Lined with jersey hot pants with a ball pocket on one leg and a phone pocket on other leg.

title: Crochet-Look Skirt
schema_description: Knee-length, crochet-look skirt. High waist, concealed zipper at back, and scalloped-edge hem with a slit at back. Unlined.

title: Flared Jersey Skirt
schema_description: Short skirt in soft jersey. Low waist, wide, foldover waistband, and gathered seam over hips. Flared hem.
